						<p>Vijayanagara, Viruppaṇṇa-Uḍaiyar, Āngirasa, Āni = A.D. 1392.</p>						

						<p>Later part not available. This seems to refer to some loan taken from the temple by Poṟkōyil-mārāyaṉ with the promise to return it in double the amount.</p>						

